  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 29eba545bae127f488175478b5cdcb00, type: 3}
  m_Name: WizardNPC
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::NpcDialogue
  npcName: Mysterious Wizard
  dialogueLines:
  - Why hello there!
  - I study the magic of Aether and Umbra Terra!
  - The fractures in our lands have caused many portals to open up around our peaceful
    little town.
  - During my research, I've found that one can only cross these portals when they
    hold a VERY SPECIFIC ammount of strange purple gems imbdued with power.
  - I went ahead and labeled them using some signs for the convenience of the people-
    the "level" corresponds to how many gems one must by holding.
  - You say you've come to seal the fracture?
  - Well, I wish you luck on your journey young one.
